.TH LPF-HISTORY 8 "June 2026" "lpf 0.2.1" "lpf Manual"
.SH NAME
lpf\-history \- show policy apply history and rollback points
.SH SYNOPSIS
lpf history
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show policy apply history, checksums, tests, operators, and rollback points.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\-\-json
emit machine\-readable history
.SH EXAMPLES
lpf history
.SH FILES
/var/lib/lpf/history
.SH SAFETY NOTES
History output must redact private host inventory.
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success.
Non\-zero when validation, planning, or host operations fail.
.SH SEE ALSO
lpf\-rollback(8), lpf\-man(8)
